                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi> The house is open all night—as I was going out of the kitchen door a woman asked me to accompany her down to Drury lane—she went into the pawnbroker's with another woman, and I remained outside—when they came out we went and had some beer, and she gave me the ticket.?</p>
